data.description: Sensational Hartford Commons 3-level, 3-bed, 4-bath townhome. Inside you'll experience a spacious foyer with natural light. Large windows and the 9' ceilings create an open airy feel. Living room features a gas fireplace. Open concept kitchen includes granite counters, HW floors, newer SS appliances, center island/breakfast bar, and eat-in kitchen. Step out onto the deck to enjoy some fresh air. Main level also has a 1/2 bath. Upper level has a spacious owner's suite, walk-in closet, en-suite bath with over-sized soaking tub. Also, there is a 2nd bedroom + full bath, a multi-use loft, and convenient 2nd-floor laundry. Lower level has the 3rd bedroom, 3/4 bath, tuck-under 2 car garage with ample storage. Plentiful closet space too. Walk to EP Mall, shopping, restaurants, parks, trails, and entertainment venues. Great freeway access for an easy commute. This townhome comes with a 1yr home warranty with HVAC coverage - offering hassle free living you don't want to miss!
